{"type": "article", "id": 20010, "title": "巧克力包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-31T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607174323PwQFJI4kOlisyTEB.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t美国的巧克力品牌 Vosges 是一个带有女性色彩的食品品牌，这组巧克力的概念包装来自一位年仅 20 岁的设计师。圆形的盒子精致小巧，像一个梳妆盒，上面用深蓝色的细线勾出蝴蝶一样的柔和图案，围着盒子的侧面有一根深蓝色的带子，也系上了蝴蝶结，成为盒子的提亮。盒子里面用亮度很高的深蓝色做背景，放上了黑色的松露巧克力，打开后有很强烈的对比和衬托。<a href=\"http://xingwei-huang-p2fi.squarespace.com/about/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是设计师的主页。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150330JZiHqEB7z5FMfr8G.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"689\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150330mBRrOiH2P5c6ltWM.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150331rhAguYwaBn4tLU3I.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"702\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150334NFykMDpC4qr2cAjL.gif\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}